{"id": "QmV3euTNy52Ai49AmqEG4pfKY5ts79EVcJb48zjWFYSaGb", "title": "[TIP 3] Reducing Minimum Loan Amount for Borrowers", "body": "\nOriginal Author(s)\nSubhajit Ray \nForum proposal - https://forum.truefi.io/t/reduce-minimum-loan-amount-for-borrowers/182\n\nSummary:\nA simple proposal to reduce the minimum loan amount to 10,000 TUSD from the current 1,000,000 TUSD. \n\nBackground:\nThis request has been put forward by borrowers and several members of our community. It will enable smaller borrowers to establish a credit history on the TrueFi platform.\n\nMotivation:\nA reduction in the minimum borrowing amount would allow the community to get to know new borrowers at a much lower risk. \n\nSpecification:\nThis proposal (if passed) will lower the minimum loan amount that borrowers can request from $1,000,000 to $10,000.\n \n", "choices": ["YES, Reduce Minimum to $10,000", "NO, Keep Current Parameters"], "start": 1610812800, "end": 1611158400, "snapshot": "11664946", "state": "closed", "author": "0x8Fac841807E21807F511dAf3C04a34cd78661F4c", "space": {"id": "truefigov.eth", "name": "TrueFi"}, "votes": 9, "votes_data": [{"id": "QmcbxKx993pR4Akd9VYvwodioU3QsoVtw8Cgo9ZdC6R6uz", "voter": "0x7De370fADcF43D12E3a7a463056606A96dB3248A", "created": 1611099496, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "truefigov.eth"}}, {"id": "QmbB5rCHkfKuyWspjZhrd2msNitmqHDbXgnWn4E2FDtMKL", "voter": "0xf91d8Ef97D5c7c08d7453D1852168fc36aa95dA4", "created": 1611095335, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "truefigov.eth"}}, {"id": "QmasfgqGKzB8cVx7DK5t5GSnMczm5BjaBbRmnKz17cK6es", "voter": "0x6f3F56f613B9960b8B7BA88b64F35337c7D27039", "created": 1611093988, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "truefigov.eth"}}, {"id": "QmfPksiHEkQoa5JdJFhYnrRZWy7qsEXBmYaMLh8HjBzWWE", "voter": "0x7657Ff00Ddc858A31B9F286AF47097B98bA4A847", "created": 1611086681, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "truefigov.eth"}}, {"id": "QmRAFgxMJ6NYaont5zFjDcP6SPQvT1Q6XorLezwyZYa5Sf", "voter": "0x005FA2741421824CdC8aCEB39687D80746aD647F", "created": 1611083339, "